%% Diagram: Token bucket vs leaky bucket — burst behavior at the edge
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    Req([Request]) --> Mode{Algorithm}

    Mode -- token bucket --> TBCheck{Token<br/>available?}
    Refill[Refiller<br/>+r tokens/sec] --> Bucket[(Bucket<br/>capacity = burst)]
    Bucket --> TBCheck
    TBCheck -- yes --> TBPass[Pass<br/>burst-friendly]
    TBCheck -- no --> TBDrop[429 Too Many Requests]

    Mode -- leaky bucket --> LBQ{Queue<br/>full?}
    LBQ -- no --> Queue[(Queue capacity)]
    LBQ -- yes --> LBDrop[429 Too Many Requests]
    Queue --> Leak[Drain at fixed rate r]
    Leak --> LBPass[Pass<br/>smoothed output]

    style TBPass fill:#cfc,stroke:#3a3
    style LBPass fill:#cfc,stroke:#3a3
    style TBDrop fill:#fcc,stroke:#a33
    style LBDrop fill:#fcc,stroke:#a33
